        <h4>Sentiment analysis on movie reviews</h4>
        <p>Analysing movie's based on user reviews and providing recommendation system by predicting their sentiments. It is a simple application using a Machine Learning model that works on a set of training data, using Random Forest Classifier to classify real time movie reviews, and design a movie recommendation system for the user based on that using Python and Cassandra.</p>
